rows.label: bf07220100_0030
rows.name:
Sorry, my lady.
I've been feeling a little dizzy...

rows.label: bf07220100_0060
rows.name:
Yes, for a little while now.
Though I'm still capable of standing.

rows.label: bf07220100_0080
rows.name:
What's up with this place?
It's kinda creepy.

rows.label: bf07220100_0120
rows.name:
The tales say that Spirit Crucible Elpys
saps the strength of Blades.

rows.label: bf07220100_0130
rows.name:
It's one of the reasons why none
have ever returned from its depths.

rows.label: bf07220100_0150
rows.name:
Ether flow scarce in this area.
That may be cause of problems.

rows.label: bf07220100_0160
rows.name: Like that time in the Luxurian palace?

rows.label: bf07220100_0180
rows.name:
Glowing particles in air...
They absorb ether. That is source of light.

rows.label: bf07220100_0190
rows.name:
So not only do you have less power,
the power you DO have is being absorbed?

rows.label: bf07220100_0220
rows.name:
Hana just fine.
Hana never better.

rows.label: bf07220100_0230
rows.name: Of course, you're an artificial Blade, ain'tcha?
